-- Daimler to invest 1.5 bln eur in Sindelfingen plant by 2020
-- By Ilona Wissenbach
-- Wed Jul 30, 2014 08:38AM EDT
-- None



FRANKFURT, July 30 (Reuters) - Daimler <DAIGn.DE> on Wednesday said it would invest 1.5 billion euros ($2 billion) in its Sindelfingen plant by 2020, after labour representatives agreed to cost and efficiency measures designed to save a triple-digit million euro amount.

